  m_text: "Battle System \nEvery monster Killed, adding virus contamination for 0,01.
    \nEvery normal monster dropped xp and gold.\nEvery level up get 3 allocated point.\nEvery
    boss monster dropped xp, gold and diamond.\nAfter 50% Contamintion, clean button
    will be shown.\nIf contamination reach 70% the debuff will be applied to the
    character\nmin debuff 10% and max debuff 30%"
